ht|q|AT|^B@2 
If the auction begins 2@C--NOT 2@D (in other words, any response other than 2@D), then all bids are natural and at least game must be reached.|
PG| ***** 27 ***** |


AT|

If the auction begins 2@C-2@D-- and opener names a suit, what happens next?|
PG| ***** 28 ***** |


NT||
